Title: Wardens' Wrath
Description:
Lord Hel'nurath's hubris gave me an opportunity to study what he's doing. I think I found a way to give us an opening to strike.

<Arko'narin glances at her brother.>

I fear this will take a lot out of Lysander. But I know he'll give it everything he has. Perhaps... perhaps my perceptions have been misplaced.

It is time to put my... our demons to rest.
ObjectivesText: Defend Lysander as he works to disrupt Lord Hel'nurath's ritual.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Lysander Starshade in Jaedenar
